title: 115 - A Cree For Help
description: On today’s show, the boys discuss several different topics ranging from new movies that are coming out from Nic Cage, Tone questions Anthony Mackie’s acting prowess, Bill takes it on the shins a few times after eating an entire bag of caramels and watching 20+ hours of a new anime show, and the guys fire through some questions for The Pod FOD. As always, submit your questions to The Pod FOD on Twitter and Instagram @ThePodPMI. We appreciate you all for listening, see you Friday.
